  "keyFeatures": [
    "Reusable UI components built on top of shadcn/ui (DateRangePicker, PhoneInput, Dropzone, Stepper)",
    "Fully typed React hooks collection (useBoolean, useDebounce, useLocalStorage, useEventListener, and more)",
    "Schema-driven form system (ShaddyForm) with react-hook-form and Zod integration",
    "Pre-built form fields covering text, password, phone, select, checkbox, date, and more",
    "Utility functions (composeProviders, createEnv) for better code organization",
    "React design patterns guide covering Container-Presentation, Hooks, Compound Components, Render Props, and more",
    "Internationalization (i18n) support via next-intl (English and Portuguese)",
    "Built with Next.js App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and Turbo monorepo"
  ],
